org.cef.callback

Interface CefJSDialogCallback


  • public interface CefJSDialogCallback
    Callback interface used for asynchronous continuation of JavaScript dialog requests.(用于异步延续JavaScript对话框请求的回调接口。)

      • Continue

        void Continue(boolean success,
              java.lang.String user_input)
        Continue the JS dialog request.(继续JS对话框请求。)
        Parameters:
        success - Set to true if the OK button was pressed.(success-如果按下OK按钮，则设置为true。)
        user_input - The value should be specified for prompt dialogs.(user_input-应该为提示对话框指定值。)
